data.text: @minastiel Tuo on ihan näppärää ainetta, jos on tarvetta saada iho puudutettua paikallisesti. 😄 Ja ymmärrän, sairaalat/terveysasemat/tmv. eivät koskaan ole kivoja paikkoja. On kuitenkin superhyvä, että otat rokotteen pelosta huolimatta! 🤗
@Starkku Oho en oo koskaa kuullukkaa tollasesta! Ei oo koskaan ennenkään rokotteet sattunu tho, pelko vaan yleisesti 😭
@savuton Thank you are the most supportive luv u ;_; ❤️

@minastiel Tsemppiä, hyvin se menee! Siellä on taitava ammattilainen laittamassa rokotteen, joten homma on tosi nopeasti ohi. ☺️ Ja jos pistäminen tuntuu ikävältä, apteekista saa reseptivapaasti Emla-voidetta, jolla voi pintapuuduttaa rokotusalueen. 👍🏻
@minastiel plus you can take it while laying down!
@minastiel this! slept like 3 hours but somehow I'm still alive so you can do it too!
@timrulezzz Yeah I believe so! Nurses are usually very warm hearted people in here ^°^

@minastiel Ah then I can imagine it not being easy to go :0 if the people who work at the place you need to get vaccinated are a bit alike the people who work there in my country then they'll be really nice to you tho so that may help a little to make you feel better ^^

Like I want to escape somewhere from my own home and avoid taking it 😭 No worries tho, I'll take it but damn I couldn't even sleep last night, it's like constant start of a panic attack I'm just trying to not let it pop up.
@timrulezzz Yeah thanks! I just have a bad phobia towards hospitals and everything in there so it's super difficult to maintain a normal mindset TAT
@minastiel I just got it and survived! Now wating if anything comes up 👏🏻 You can do it!!! 💕

@minastiel It'll be over soon! the injection itself doesn't take more than a few seconds and you barely feel it ^^ As for the scary side effects worst thing that is gonna happen is you feel a little sick for a few days probably but there's a chance you won't even notice anything :D
